{
  "version": 1,
  "course": {
    "id": "nce2-039-am-i-all-right",
    "title": "Lesson 39: Am I All Right",
    "audioFilename": "39－Am I All Right.mp3",
    "duration": 94.981,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.34,
      "end": 1.92,
      "text": "Lesson 39.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第39课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 2.96,
      "end": 4.3,
      "text": "Am I All Right?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我是否痊愈？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 5.72,
      "end": 8.8,
      "text": "First listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 10.68,
      "end": 11.62,
      "text": "Why did Mr. Gilbert",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "吉尔伯特先生"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 12.1,
      "end": 13.58,
      "text": "telephone Dr.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "为什么给米灵顿医生"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 13.86,
      "end": 14.32,
      "text": "Millington?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "打电话？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 16.46,
      "end": 25.22,
      "text": "While John Gilbert was in hospital, he asked his doctor to tell him whether his operation had been successful.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "约翰·吉尔伯特住院期间，请医生告诉他手术是否成功。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 26.1,
      "end": 28.94,
      "text": "But the doctor refused to do so.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "但医生拒绝告诉他。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 29.9,
      "end": 34.74,
      "text": "The following day, the patient asked for a bedside telephone.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第二天，病人要了一部床头电话。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 35.86,
      "end": 42.5,
      "text": "When he was alone, he telephoned the hospital exchange and asked for Dr.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "独处时，他打电话给医院总机，要求接通米灵顿"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 42.72,
      "end": 43.1,
      "text": "Millington.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "医生。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 44.34,
      "end": 47.48,
      "text": "When the doctor answered the phone, Mr. Gilbert",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "医生接电话后，吉尔伯特先生"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 47.96,
      "end": 53.22,
      "text": "said he was inquiring about a certain patient, a Mr.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "说他想询问一位病人的情况，一位"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 53.78,
      "end": 54.28,
      "text": "Gilbert.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "吉尔伯特先生。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 55.23,
      "end": 56.9,
      "text": "He asked if Mr.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他问吉尔伯特先生"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 57.24,
      "end": 63.16,
      "text": "Gilbert's operation had been successful, and the doctor told him that it had been.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "的手术是否成功，医生告诉他手术很成功。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 64.84,
      "end": 66.76,
      "text": "He then asked when Mr. Gilbert",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "接着他又问吉尔伯特先生"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 67.22,
      "end": 75.66,
      "text": "would be allowed to go home, and the doctor told him that he would have to stay in hospital for another two weeks.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "什么时候可以回家，医生告诉他还得在医院住两个星期。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 76.88,
      "end": 77.88,
      "text": "Then Dr.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "随后米灵顿"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "start": 78.14,
      "end": 82.58,
      "text": "Millington asked the caller if he was a relative of the patient.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "医生问打电话的人是否是病人的亲属。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "start": 82.58,
      "end": 85.74,
      "text": "No, the patient answered.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“不是，”病人回答，"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "start": 86.58,
      "end": 87.98,
      "text": "I am Mr.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“我就是吉尔伯特"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "start": 88.44,
      "end": 88.84,
      "text": "Gilbert.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "先生。”"
      }
    }
  ]
}
